{
  "texts": [
    "AI cannot be listed as an author since it cannot be accountable for the work.",
    "Journals should require authors to disclose AI-assisted technologies (e.g., LLMs, chatbots) upon submission, specifying the AI's role in writing assistance, data collection, analysis, or figure generation.",
    "33 Use of disclosure statements like \"The authors acknowledge the use of 'GPT name' for assisting in the drafting of the manuscript.",
    "The final content was reviewed and edited by the authors\" is encouraged.",
    "Authors must disclose the use of AI tools in manuscript preparation, detailing the extent and nature of the assistance."
  ]
}